            <abstract>
                <p>
                    A sub-type of <ref type="authFile" corresp="GweltDeed">gwǝlt-document</ref> which is clearly identifiable is the “renovation”
                    of the former grant with the formula
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐደስኩ᎓…</foreign> or
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">አግባእኩ፡ ...</foreign> etc.
                    The former grant may also be repeated in whatever form, with the name of the king, with the word <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጐለተ</foreign>.
                    The Liber axumae includes quite a number of them.
                </p>
